{"word":"G5275 - ὑπολείπω - hypoleípō - hoop-ol-i'-po - Be left","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπολείπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypoleípō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-ol-i'-po</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be left</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மீதியாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to leave behind"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5295 - ὑποτρέχω - hypotréchō - hoop-ot-rekh'-o/5295\">G5295</a> and <a href=\"#/G3007 - λείπω - leípō - li'-po/3007\">G3007</a>; to <i>leave under</i> (<i>behind</i>), that is, (passively) to <i>remain</i> (<i>survive</i>): - be left.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}